lyrics:
[Verse]
In the depths of darkness, where shadows creep
A requiem for a death, hauntingly deep
Melancholy melodies, echoes of despair
Spiraling in the air, a soul laid bare

[Chorus]
Requiem for a death, a somber refrain
Piercing through our hearts, invoking pain
The chorus of loss, whispered in the night
Requiem for a death, guiding our plight
